data.description: Located in the heart of East Bernard this charming 1917 home features high ceilings,crown molding,&spacious porch views.Enjoy sitting on the back porch to enjoy the beautiful sunsets that our beautiful sky’s have to offer.An inviting saltwater heated pool/jacuzzi with light features surrounding the beautiful travertine deck&several spots for a cozy fire pit.You will not find another property quite like this!Sitting on 0.50 acre with main house at 3bdrm,full bath&a spacious guest suite with a kitchen,full bathroom&a MiniSplit wall A/C unit. Laundry room in the second living space.On the property is a shed to store all your item completed with electric&a window unit.The Kitchen has a warm welcoming feel to cook your family meals.HVAC was recently serviced.Front of the home is adorned with majestic,hundred-year-old Oak trees providing shade and a serene ambiance Don’t miss the opportunity to be located in the heart of a small town in a peaceful and quiet neighborhood.
